The birth of my said brother HARJIBHAI on 6th February 914 at Anandpura, Taluka Sankheda, District Baroda, GU jarat State, India was not registered in NOTARIAL the birth registry at Anandpura, Taluka Sankheda, district Baroda, Gujarat State, India as such registration was not compulsory at that time.
